org.apache.lucene.mockfile

Class FilterSecureDirectoryStream<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.lucene.mockfile.FilterSecureDirectoryStream<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable, Iterable<T>, DirectoryStream<T>, SecureDirectoryStream<T>

    public class FilterSecureDirectoryStream<T>
extends Object
implements SecureDirectoryStream<T>
    A FilterSecureDirectoryStream contains another SecureDirectoryStream, which it uses as its basic source of data, possibly transforming the data along the way or providing additional functionality.
